The initial consideration is Pounds 7.13m. There are two tranches of up to
Pounds 2.36m and Pounds 6.4m in deferred consideration should profits reach
certain targets. If the entire deferred consideration was to become payable
then Douthwaite's pre-tax profits in 1996 would be some Pounds 6m.
In 1991 Douthwaite made a pre-tax profit of Pounds 1.61m from sales of
Pounds 14.4m.
