shareholders' funds of Pounds 11.6m and net cash of Pounds 3.2m. No interest
was capitalised in the past year.
'We remain in an excellent position to continue our expansion plans in the
year ahead,' he stated. The 60-bed nursing home at Trowbridge was expected
to open in the final quarter.
